    {"type":"text","id":"zdB1t","x":136,"y":982,"width":530,"height":140,"text":"at end of each entry (_applyAndExecute):\n\n  _rollingHash == entry.rollingHash\n        → RollingHashMismatch\n  _currentL2ToL1Call == l2ToL1Calls.length\n        → UnconsumedL2ToL1Calls\n  _lastL1ToL2CallConsumed == expectedL1ToL2Calls.length\n        → UnconsumedL1ToL2Calls","originalText":"at end of each entry (_applyAndExecute):\n\n  _rollingHash == entry.rollingHash\n        → RollingHashMismatch\n  _currentL2ToL1Call == l2ToL1Calls.length\n        → UnconsumedL2ToL1Calls\n  _lastL1ToL2CallConsumed == expectedL1ToL2Calls.length\n        → UnconsumedL1ToL2Calls","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#bfdbfe","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":400012,"version":1,"versionNonce":400013,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.45},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"zdB2","x":710,"y":968,"width":440,"height":166,"strokeColor":"#1e40af","backgroundColor":"#dbeafe","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":400020,"version":1,"versionNonce":400021,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":[{"id":"zdB2t","type":"text"}],"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"zdB2t","x":726,"y":982,"width":410,"height":140,"text":"State-delta backstop\n\nStateDelta.currentState is checked against\nrollups[rid].stateRoot at consumption time;\nmismatch reverts StateRootMismatch.\n\nThis is what lets per-rollup queues interleave\nconsumption across rollups safely.","originalText":"State-delta backstop\n\nStateDelta.currentState is checked against\nrollups[rid].stateRoot at consumption time;\nmismatch reverts StateRootMismatch.\n\nThis is what lets per-rollup queues interleave\nconsumption across rollups safely.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#1e40af","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":400022,"version":1,"versionNonce":400023,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.3},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"zdB3","x":1180,"y":968,"width":380,"height":166,"strokeColor":"#1e40af","backgroundColor":"#dbeafe","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":400030,"version":1,"versionNonce":400031,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":[{"id":"zdB3t","type":"text"}],"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"zdB3t","x":1196,"y":982,"width":350,"height":140,"text":"Ether accounting (per entry)\n\ntotalEtherDelta ==\n     entryEtherIn − etherOut\n        → EtherDeltaMismatch\n\nrevertSpan calls count toward neither —\ntheir transfers are rolled back.","originalText":"Ether accounting (per entry)\n\ntotalEtherDelta ==\n     entryEtherIn − etherOut\n        → EtherDeltaMismatch\n\nrevertSpan calls count toward neither —\ntheir transfers are rolled back.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#1e40af","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":400032,"version":1,"versionNonce":400033,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.3},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"zdB4","x":1590,"y":968,"width":540,"height":166,"strokeColor":"#dc2626","backgroundColor":"#fee2e2","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":400040,"version":1,"versionNonce":400041,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":[{"id":"zdB4t","type":"text"}],"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"zdB4t","x":1606,"y":982,"width":510,"height":140,"text":"Comms over-claim guards\n\n• Synchronous cross-rollup is BOUNDED — atomic\n   only between rollups verified TOGETHER in one batch.\n• Same-block consumption required (lastVerifiedBlock).\n• Multi-prover CAPABLE — threshold is per-rollup, not a fixed floor.\n• Status: living docs, pre-final; 2 MEDIUM findings open.","originalText":"Comms over-claim guards\n\n• Synchronous cross-rollup is BOUNDED — atomic\n   only between rollups verified TOGETHER in one batch.\n• Same-block consumption required (lastVerifiedBlock).\n• Multi-prover CAPABLE — threshold is per-rollup, not a fixed floor.\n• Status: living docs, pre-final; 2 MEDIUM findings open.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#b91c1c","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":400042,"version":1,"versionNonce":400043,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.35}
